Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:04.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 明天開始放暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:06.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但不要玩得太瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:12.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:14.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:17.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明天一起去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:18.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:21.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}突然想吃西瓜了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:22.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:23.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那算啥呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:24.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,去噴西瓜子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:25.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好啊好啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,騎車帶人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:07.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明天開始放暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:11.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯 是期盼已久的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:14.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不用上學 我可以玩個盡興啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:16.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要好好做作業哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你肯定想著明天是暑假的第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,作業就先放到一邊對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:22.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被我猜對了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:27.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但不好好享受暑假怎麼行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:32.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一想到要去游泳池 還要去海水浴或者野營之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,時間就完全不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:38.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是一直都是暑假就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:39.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:41.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也挺喜歡上學的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:43.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:48.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:52.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暑假嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:55.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:56.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,風吹得好涼快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再騎快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,別為難我了 太熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們也試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,當然 西片坐前面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 這種事情不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看會遇上汽車什麼的 太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:27.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但這裡汽車走不了 也不是校道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:32.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 難道你害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:35.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你是不會騎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,騎車帶人而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 太危險了所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我們去空地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,如果你失敗了 就要請我喝果汁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:58.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給我瞧好了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:03:59.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,區區騎車帶人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 剛剛的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要請果汁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:16.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,騎車帶人有這麼難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:20.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 你沒有故意使絆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:21.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:22.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只是正常地坐著而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,做不到都是西片的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:29.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:32.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,之前我坐別人的自行車的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:34.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個人騎得很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:39.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是女性朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:42.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:43.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:52.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再來一次 就差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:55.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,下一次一定可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡啊 心裡突然有些不爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:04:59.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:06.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有 只是不想請果汁而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯 只是我不想請果汁罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哦 前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:21.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最後一次和我兩個人一起騎車的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:22.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:25.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好像是四歲的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:34.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:43.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片不買果汁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:52.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我…就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:55.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好意思說沒錢給自己買了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:05:58.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:09.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正你又打算拿間接接吻什麼的來捉弄我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:12.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,別逞強了 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:17.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:22.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這種時候需要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:28.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給你 別中暑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:30.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可以拿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:31.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:34.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:39.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片一提到間接接吻就會臉紅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:44.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是因為這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:46.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:48.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:51.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:55.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:01.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暫時不能一起放學回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那是因為暑假到了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:07.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:11.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明天開始 中午之前在這裡練習騎車帶人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼？我倒是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:15.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是不可以上公路哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 在這裡騎就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:21.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只在這裡騎的話 練習不就沒有意義了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:23.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 有意義哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:26.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:29.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明天開始就是暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:37.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好了 那我們回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:41.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暑假嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:45.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真期待暑假呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在才這麼想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暑假第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒想到暑假的第一天就下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:08:00.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的暑假計劃全毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:02.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才一天而已 沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,本來要今天去的泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:07.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要怎麼補回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:08.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你別哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:12.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然下雨那也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啦 開始做作業吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:15.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「誒」什麼啊 你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不會沒帶作業過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:23.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不是說了下雨不能出去玩 不如做作業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還以為聽錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:26.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再說明明是暑假為什麼會有作業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不覺得奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:34.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,假日不應該休息才對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:35.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然有那也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:50.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:53.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉也別做作業 一起來癱著無所事事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是眼前有人在做作業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:57.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就會讓我想起作業 根本享受不起來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:09:00.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,關我啥事 話說你倒是給我想起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:02.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這才第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:05.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,作業什麼的就別管了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:12.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是會在8月31日哭的典型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:14.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你這個石頭腦袋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:17.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,夠了 我要看漫畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:24.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:25.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:29.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以用漫畫來寫閱讀感想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:30.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:33.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你們趕緊給我回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,試膽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了 終於天晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說我在高興什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:56.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:04.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:07.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為我們不是約好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:12.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:19.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到處都是水窪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:22.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,昨晚下大雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一時間我還沒認出來是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:29.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來 雖然在休息日和她也遇過幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,和她約出來玩還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:36.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道這就是所謂的約會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不 才不是這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:40.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這只是騎車帶人的練習而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:43.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:46.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在聽我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣子沒法練習騎車帶人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:58.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我原本計劃中午直接出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:03.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,回家太麻煩了 到中午之前就陪我打發時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這就是…約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:14.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊 不要去人太多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:18.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是被同級的人看見了 不知道他們會說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:20.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:22.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:26.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,試膽？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:28.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很有夏天的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一般不是晚上玩的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:34.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒關係啦 裡面還挺黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且這裡 聽說會出現哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,會出現什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:47.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這條隧道本來是直通的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:50.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,卻經常發生車輛撞上牆壁的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:53.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這才被迫在旁邊修了一條新的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,從此以後每晚都會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:03.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒有了車輛作為獵物的嗜血幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:05.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:09.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這附近還有神隱的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:13.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有時候 人會「呼」的一聲消失不見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:16.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說 你害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:22.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且現在可是大白天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這種東西一點也不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:32.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比想像中還要黑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:38.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺聽到了奇怪的風聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:42.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,符咒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:45.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是護身符吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:46.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這裡有些什麼不好的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:54.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片你害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:56.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的 剛剛的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這次又是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:05.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼這裡會有油桶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:06.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:09.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,去看看裡面有什麼吧 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:12.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:15.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誰怕了 看就看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我去看總行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:41.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:44.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:45.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學？你在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,別耍我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:14:00.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來 她剛剛有說過神隱什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:01.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:05.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 快回話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:17.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你慌什麼呢 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:22.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你剛才在找我對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看上去像是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這就是她的目的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎 你看那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:35.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有一個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,去看看裡面有什麼吧 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可不會重複中同樣的招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,別小看我了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,拔 拔不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的手拔不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:49.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的演技怎麼樣啊高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來吧 害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:55.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 我好像被什麼東西扯住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:56.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快來幫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:15:00.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西…片…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:02.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被嚇到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:04.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:06.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是掉在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,手 能拔出來真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:13.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:15.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們走著瞧 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:16.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,下一次我一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你太大驚小怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:25.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,出來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:28.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 一次也沒能報復成功
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊 哥哥你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:33.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又有情侶在隧道約會了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要說了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:36.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:41.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,他們說是約會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到底在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:47.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的臉好紅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,試膽真好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:55.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:58.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快到中午了 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:15:59.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說的也對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:01.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要去哪裡 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又要走那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你害怕嗎 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:19.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天的份完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:22.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 明明是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:25.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,俯臥撐的數量卻完全沒少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:28.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,自由研究
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 清湯味挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你騙人 眼淚都要出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:38.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不 我覺得比早苗的昆布味好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:39.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,半斤八兩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:41.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明有這麼多口味可以挑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不明白你們為什麼要選那兩種
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:45.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉的西瓜味太沒新意了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,正所謂冒險才是青春 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:51.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,選個冰棍也算冒險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:54.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比起這個 你們倆決定好自由研究要做什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:56.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:57.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也還在考慮中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有什麼比較輕鬆的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一天就能做完的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你倒是好好研究啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,狗的觀察日記如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:14.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個不錯 聽上去很簡單的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:17.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正每天的行動都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:19.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,複印後把日期改下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:22.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,至少給我努力用手寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:24.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且狗的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不就是吠著要你起床之後帶它去散步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:29.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,吠著要你給它餵食 然後睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:33.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,吠著要你陪它玩 然後又吠著要吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,根本沒有研究的意義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉真是死板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:40.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘛 人家是年級委員嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:42.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真拿她沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:44.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這兩個傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:48.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說你們 寫作業了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:52.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,時間還多得是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:53.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:58.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話先說在前頭 我不會給你們抄的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:02.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,作為交換 我們幫你做自由研究吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是關於狗的吧 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:05.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然你總說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到最後還是會借給我們看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:08.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,人家是年級委員嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:13.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的自由研究就觀察這兩個傢伙好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:16.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,水管
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:25.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天真是暑假裡最倒霉的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上睡過頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後自行車還爆胎了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:39.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天沒有騎車帶人的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:42.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學說她和家人去旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是今天回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:46.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:49.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我難得忍住中午出去玩的衝動幫忙做家務
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:51.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還被派去跑腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:54.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這暑假真是倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天的一句話日記就這樣寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:18:58.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:02.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個背影…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:05.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:09.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,已經回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:13.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 悄悄地跟在她後面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:18.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說不定還能發現她的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:36.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺剛剛她往這邊看了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 應該是錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被她發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:44.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是我看到你的帽子了哦 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你打算嚇唬我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:48.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就讓我先發制人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在一句話日記裡寫上好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:59.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,中 中計了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:01.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:04.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被叫去超市買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:07.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真巧啊 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你載著我一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都說了 不可以騎車帶人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:13.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她什麼時候發現我在跟蹤她的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:17.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,小心 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:24.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:27.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,果然今天真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:30.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:33.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒事 這種程度放著不管就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:36.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不行 一定要洗一洗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:46.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太糗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:48.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有那麼疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:49.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只是在想今天本來就運氣差了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:54.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還受了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:57.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是個糟透了的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:02.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 日記作業要寫什麼才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:02.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:06.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,會弄髒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:08.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你就別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:11.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:25.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好涼快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:30.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你剛才是想要幫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:32.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:35.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片也過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:37.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,涼涼的很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:39.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:41.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來吧來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:46.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很涼快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:48.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:52.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我覺得今天的暑假很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:55.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為遇到了某人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:59.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:01.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明天給你帶手信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:02.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:06.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要啊高木同學 好涼啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:30.51,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:34.93,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:45.27,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:54.07,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:01:02.37,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:05.33,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:10.71,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:14.59,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.51,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:26.60,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:34.90,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:40.33,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:44.29,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:54.55,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:30.51,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:34.93,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:45.27,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:54.07,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校園的庭院 第一個發現你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:01:02.37,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你說些什麼呢 即便是想著這些也是一種樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:05.33,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗簾隨風起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:10.71,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不經意地投入一束陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:14.59,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美麗的容顏笑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.51,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:26.60,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風兒喧囂 似要吹散考試的憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:34.90,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}吶 我想要和你一起 立下兩人的秘密約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:40.33,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:44.29,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:54.55,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.03,0:22:25.74,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}プールサイドで　夢を見ていたの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:31.58,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しいほどに　あなたの声が響いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:35.91,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}響いてるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:40.75,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}昨日のあたし　まるで子猫なの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:46.47,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}かすかに分かる　白い毛並みが震えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:50.68,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}震えてるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:58.60,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}それが恋をしていた日　あなたを好きな日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.65,0:23:02.52,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ　忘れないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:09.53,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}恋していた　あたしのこと　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:14.54,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}自転車こいで　海を見に行く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:18.37,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}夜明けの空に　太陽をめがけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.37,0:23:22.13,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}飾らない日の　おしゃべりは続き
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.13,0:23:29.72,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}自転車こいで　太陽をめがけて
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.03,0:22:25.74,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在泳池邊上 做了一個美夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:31.58,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你的聲音響起 讓我如痴如醉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:35.91,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}響徹耳畔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:40.75,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}昨天的我 宛如一隻幼貓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:46.47,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}隱約還記得 白色的皮毛顫抖著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:50.68,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}顫抖不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:58.60,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}那是我墜入愛河的一天 是我愛上你的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.65,0:23:02.52,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}吶 請不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:09.53,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}墜入愛河的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:14.54,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}踏上自行車去看海吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:18.37,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在拂曉的天空朝太陽奔去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.37,0:23:22.13,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不需修飾的日子裡繼續聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.13,0:23:29.72,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}踏上自行車奔向太陽
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——STAFF——
